1
00:01:42,708 --> 00:01:46,041
[NARRATOR] The dismal concrete
jungle of the Furutama Projects.

2
00:01:46,125 --> 00:01:47,750
An underworld
industrial district

3
00:01:47,833 --> 00:01:49,500
built by Omura Industries.

4
00:01:49,583 --> 00:01:52,625
Amid these identical towers
of brick and steel,

5
00:01:52,708 --> 00:01:55,125
hope cannot be found.

6
00:01:59,458 --> 00:02:01,041
[engine revs]

7
00:02:03,833 --> 00:02:04,916
[beeping]

8
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:07,291
[NANCY] Jose-san,
this is Nancy calling.

9
00:02:07,375 --> 00:02:10,291
The mission is proceeding
as planned. Over.

10
00:02:10,375 --> 00:02:12,291
[JOSE] Listen. You gotta
quit playing around

11
00:02:12,375 --> 00:02:13,958
with all the cloak
and dagger crap.

12
00:02:14,041 --> 00:02:15,416
This is serious, ya know?

13
00:02:15,500 --> 00:02:16,916
And if you blow
this one you're screwed.

14
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:20,541
You're a real charmer.
I appreciate it.

15
00:02:21,291 --> 00:02:22,958
[tires screech]

16
00:02:23,041 --> 00:02:24,416
[NANCY]
Building fourteen, right?

17
00:02:24,500 --> 00:02:28,750
[JOSE] Yes, sixth floor.
That's the story, at least.

18
00:02:28,833 --> 00:02:31,625
But something seems
fishy about it to me.

19
00:02:40,291 --> 00:02:45,750
[footsteps]

20
00:02:45,833 --> 00:02:47,750
[NANCY]
Room 606?

21
00:02:48,916 --> 00:02:49,875
Jose-san?

22
00:02:49,958 --> 00:02:51,666
[door creaks]

23
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:54,125
[NANCY]
It's open.

24
00:02:54,208 --> 00:02:55,791
[gasps]

25
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:00,875
[grunts]

26
00:03:02,625 --> 00:03:05,208
[gasps]

27
00:03:06,333 --> 00:03:09,000
Jose-san.
Bad news! It's Taragi!

28
00:03:09,083 --> 00:03:10,208
[MAN]
Bite!

29
00:03:10,291 --> 00:03:12,000
[yells]

30
00:03:14,166 --> 00:03:17,875
[NANCY gasps, groans]

31
00:03:20,916 --> 00:03:24,458
[MAN] Now squeeze
the little rat!

32
00:03:28,583 --> 00:03:29,916
[NANCY whimpers]
[MAN chuckles]

33
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,666
[MAN]
Having trouble moving?

34
00:03:31,750 --> 00:03:34,166
[NANCY gasps]

35
00:03:34,250 --> 00:03:36,791
Feel the venom pulsing
through your veins!

36
00:03:36,875 --> 00:03:38,375
Now, come back, my pretty!

37
00:03:38,458 --> 00:03:40,083
[SNAKE hisses]

38
00:03:40,166 --> 00:03:42,500
Domo. Nancy Lee-san.

39
00:03:42,583 --> 00:03:45,125
I am the one
they call Cockatrice.

40
00:03:45,208 --> 00:03:47,375
[NANCY] How does
he know my name?

41
00:03:47,458 --> 00:03:48,875
The man in your ear.

42
00:03:48,958 --> 00:03:52,541
Jose-san has been working with
the Soukaiya for a while.

43
00:03:52,625 --> 00:03:54,791
Now be a good
little girl,

44
00:03:54,875 --> 00:03:56,791
and tell me why
a hot chick like you

45
00:03:56,875 --> 00:03:59,791
is snooping around
this place. Huh?

46
00:03:59,875 --> 00:04:02,333
[NINJA SLAYER]
Domo, Cockatrice-san.

47
00:04:02,416 --> 00:04:04,583
I am Ninja Slayer.

48
00:04:07,333 --> 00:04:10,250
Domo. Ninja Slayer-san.

49
00:04:10,333 --> 00:04:12,375
I am the one
they call Cockatrice.

50
00:04:12,458 --> 00:04:14,416
Why are you snooping
around this place?

51
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:15,583
No reason.

52
00:04:15,666 --> 00:04:17,791
But now I am here
to kill you!

53
00:04:17,875 --> 00:04:18,833
[COCKATRICE]
Bite!

54
00:04:18,916 --> 00:04:20,291
[NINJA SLAYER]
Yeeart!

55
00:04:22,708 --> 00:04:25,000
So all the rumors
about you are true.

56
00:04:25,083 --> 00:04:27,666
You're a hard rat
to kill. Until now!

57
00:04:27,750 --> 00:04:29,375
I'm gonna fill you
so full of poison

58
00:04:29,458 --> 00:04:31,375
that your head'll explode.

59
00:04:31,458 --> 00:04:33,000
[NARRATOR]
I can't believe my eyes!

60
00:04:33,083 --> 00:04:35,250
This man is some sort of
human animal hybrid!

61
00:04:35,333 --> 00:04:39,708
Instead of arms, he has
twin cobras! Scary!

62
00:04:39,791 --> 00:04:42,041
Only the most badass
ninjas can survive

63
00:04:42,125 --> 00:04:44,625
Dr. Lee's reptile
augmentation surgery,

64
00:04:44,708 --> 00:04:47,166
and master the
Daija Bite attack!

65
00:04:47,250 --> 00:04:49,750
That's why I'm
the only one around!

66
00:04:49,833 --> 00:04:51,791
Does the Soukaiya
train all their ninjas

67
00:04:51,875 --> 00:04:54,458
to deliver these
long-winded introductions?

68
00:04:54,541 --> 00:04:56,958
Come on!
Let's get to the action!

69
00:04:57,041 --> 00:04:59,666
[COCKATRICE] Sink your fangs
into his flesh, my pets!

70
00:04:59,750 --> 00:05:02,250
Psyche!
Constrictor attack!

71
00:05:02,333 --> 00:05:05,083
My twin serpents will
keep on squeezing you

72
00:05:05,166 --> 00:05:07,333
until you're nice and tender!

73
00:05:07,416 --> 00:05:09,791
And then I'm gonna
swallow you whole!

74
00:05:09,875 --> 00:05:11,041
Blaaah!

75
00:05:11,125 --> 00:05:12,833
[NINJA SLAYER]
Wasshoi!

76
00:05:12,916 --> 00:05:15,500
[COCKATRICE]
Aaaargh!

77
00:05:15,583 --> 00:05:23,291
Aaaargh! Aaaargh!
Aaaargh! Aaaargh!

78
00:05:23,375 --> 00:05:26,375
[panting]

79
00:05:27,916 --> 00:05:29,125
[NINJA SLAYER]
Who will feed you now that

80
00:05:29,208 --> 00:05:31,791
your precious "pets"
are gone?

81
00:05:31,875 --> 00:05:33,166
[COCKATRICE groans]

82
00:05:33,250 --> 00:05:35,000
Maybe this Dr. Lee
can get you in

83
00:05:35,083 --> 00:05:38,916
for another surgery. I hear
he has a waiting room.

84
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:41,583
Down in Hell! Yeeart!

85
00:05:41,666 --> 00:05:44,541
[COCKATRICE]
Sayonara!

86
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,458
This has gotta be some
kinda crazy nightmare!

87
00:05:59,708 --> 00:06:01,083
[gulps]

88
00:06:01,166 --> 00:06:03,833
[NANCY] I don't normally accept
drugs from strange men.

89
00:06:03,916 --> 00:06:06,333
It hasn't been very long
since you were bitten.

90
00:06:06,416 --> 00:06:10,000
That pill should counteract
the venom very soon.

91
00:06:10,083 --> 00:06:11,208
What's going on here?

92
00:06:11,291 --> 00:06:13,041
Who killed Taragi Wei?
Who are--

93
00:06:13,125 --> 00:06:16,166
Domo, I am
called Ninja Slayer.

94
00:06:16,250 --> 00:06:18,583
Nancy-san, you should
stop playing detective

95
00:06:18,666 --> 00:06:21,416
and flee to Kyoto right away!

96
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:23,791
The syndicate is heartless.

97
00:06:23,875 --> 00:06:25,583
They will murder you!

98
00:06:25,666 --> 00:06:27,750
Answer my question!

99
00:06:29,291 --> 00:06:31,166
Damn it!

100
00:06:32,208 --> 00:06:41,041
[mellow electronic music plays]

101
00:06:41,125 --> 00:06:43,833
[NANCY] Tanuki. I have a
hunch that that's the key

102
00:06:43,916 --> 00:06:46,791
to finding the truth about
this mess once and for all.

103
00:06:48,666 --> 00:06:51,208
[NANCY] And maybe even
the truth about him.

104
00:06:51,291 --> 00:06:53,875
[engine revs]

105
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:59,500
[long beep]

106
00:07:03,625 --> 00:07:15,875
[BIRDS cawing]

107
00:07:15,958 --> 00:07:17,875
[inhales deeply]

108
00:07:17,958 --> 00:07:20,666
[exhales deeply]

109
00:07:20,750 --> 00:07:23,041
[inhales deeply]

110
00:07:23,125 --> 00:07:25,833
[exhales deeply]

111
00:07:25,916 --> 00:07:30,875
[cawing continues]

112
00:07:49,083 --> 00:07:52,833
[CROW caws]

113
00:07:56,416 --> 00:07:57,500
[MAN 2]
Domo.

114
00:07:57,583 --> 00:07:59,625
[NINJA SLAYER grunts]
Yeeart!

115
00:07:59,708 --> 00:08:02,250
Domo. I am Ninja Slayer.

116
00:08:07,541 --> 00:08:09,458
That is quite
an impressive title.

117
00:08:09,541 --> 00:08:11,791
Pleasure to meet you.

118
00:08:11,875 --> 00:08:13,916
Domo Ninja Slayer-san.

119
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,833
I am just a simple man.

120
00:08:15,916 --> 00:08:18,708
My name is
Sugawarano Tomihide.

121
00:08:18,791 --> 00:08:20,833
[NINJA SLAYER]
Sugawarano-san, I have a favor

122
00:08:20,916 --> 00:08:22,583
I must ask you.

123
00:08:22,666 --> 00:08:26,750
Please sir. I ask that
you forget we ever met.

124
00:08:26,833 --> 00:08:30,583
Buddha sees all, but
these crows and I do not.

125
00:08:30,666 --> 00:08:31,875
[NINJA SLAYER]
But you did, in fact,

126
00:08:31,958 --> 00:08:34,250
spot me perching overhead.

127
00:08:34,333 --> 00:08:35,958
[SUGAWARANO]
Yes, but I didn't notice you

128
00:08:36,041 --> 00:08:38,750
out of pure suspicion;
it was something else.

129
00:08:38,833 --> 00:08:40,916
I sensed "good."

130
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,583
This world
has many who only

131
00:08:42,666 --> 00:08:45,333
concern themselves with
their own discomforts,

132
00:08:45,416 --> 00:08:48,458
but few who would stop
to aid an injured bird.

133
00:08:48,541 --> 00:08:49,958
[NINJA SLAYER]
Domo.

134
00:08:52,875 --> 00:08:54,500
So I don't frighten you?

135
00:08:54,583 --> 00:08:56,916
I am a ninja, after all.

136
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,625
I've lived many years.

137
00:08:58,708 --> 00:09:00,000
And full ones, at that.

138
00:09:00,083 --> 00:09:03,208
Not much frightens
me these days.

139
00:09:03,291 --> 00:09:05,625
Besides, I told you
that I could sense

140
00:09:05,708 --> 00:09:08,541
the goodness in you
earlier, remember?

141
00:09:08,625 --> 00:09:10,958
Ah. Let me
show you something.

142
00:09:11,041 --> 00:09:13,125
A picture of my family.

143
00:09:13,208 --> 00:09:15,541
The happiest
point in my life.

144
00:09:15,625 --> 00:09:17,666
My wife passed away soon after.

145
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:21,666
And my son left home to follow
his dreams without me.

146
00:09:21,750 --> 00:09:23,083
Is that so?

147
00:09:23,166 --> 00:09:27,291
Have you not heard from
your son since that day?

148
00:09:27,375 --> 00:09:28,708
Well, you see,

149
00:09:28,791 --> 00:09:31,333
he always wanted
to go off to university.

150
00:09:31,416 --> 00:09:34,541
But for some reason he
failed his entrance exams.

151
00:09:34,625 --> 00:09:37,500
So he set off for
the Kyoto republic.

152
00:09:37,583 --> 00:09:40,000
Many years passed.
Then one day,

153
00:09:40,083 --> 00:09:41,750
I received a
message saying he was

154
00:09:41,833 --> 00:09:44,708
working for Murasaki
Shikibu Cosmetics.

155
00:09:44,791 --> 00:09:46,875
I have heard
about this corporation.

156
00:09:46,958 --> 00:09:49,375
A titan in the
cosmetics industry.

157
00:09:49,458 --> 00:09:51,958
They do have
quite the reputation.

158
00:09:52,041 --> 00:09:54,833
From that day on,
every now and then,

159
00:09:54,916 --> 00:09:57,958
some money is deposited
into my bank account.

160
00:09:58,041 --> 00:10:00,500
That is most honorable.

161
00:10:00,583 --> 00:10:02,541
I suppose it is.

162
00:10:02,625 --> 00:10:05,666
But truthfully, I believe
spending time together

163
00:10:05,750 --> 00:10:07,625
would be far more valuable.

164
00:10:07,708 --> 00:10:09,083
But I wouldn't
want to interfere with

165
00:10:09,166 --> 00:10:14,000
his work or the life he's
created, so here we are.

166
00:10:18,416 --> 00:10:20,000
You've suffered
many hardships,

167
00:10:20,083 --> 00:10:23,083
yet I can't sense a hint
of murderous rage.

168
00:10:23,166 --> 00:10:27,083
How is that? Do you
practice the tea ceremony?

169
00:10:27,166 --> 00:10:30,000
[SUGAWARANO laughs]
I'm afraid I don't practice

170
00:10:30,083 --> 00:10:32,791
any intricate rituals
like that, my friend.

171
00:10:32,875 --> 00:10:35,708
To be honest, I don't
even drink much tea.

172
00:10:35,791 --> 00:10:37,208
It doesn't matter.

173
00:10:37,291 --> 00:10:39,833
You just struck me
as one who does.

174
00:10:41,416 --> 00:10:43,666
Well, I should
be taking my leave.

175
00:10:43,750 --> 00:10:46,458
Sayonara, Sugawarano-san.

176
00:10:46,541 --> 00:10:49,625
Ninja Slayer-san.
When tomorrow comes,

177
00:10:49,708 --> 00:10:53,958
will I be able to find you
perched on the tower again?

178
00:10:54,041 --> 00:10:58,041
[NINJA SLAYER] No.
Take care of yourself.

179
00:10:58,125 --> 00:11:00,083
[SUGAWARANO]
You do the same.

